InstalledItem.Name: MSD-313 Missile Rack
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Missile Rack
Manufacturer: Behring
Size: 3
Missiles: 1xS3

Behring’s MSD-313 "Marsden" is a complete ordnance storage and deployment system that can be mounted on any compatible size 3 hardpoint for the reliable and effective launch of one S3 missile.

InstalledItem.Name: Colossus Bomb
InstalledItem.Description:
Manufacturer: FireStorm Kinetics
Item Type: Explosive Bomb
Size: 10

Foes below won't stand a chance against a Colossus. FireStorm Kinetics designed this massive S10 bomb to devastate ground targets, whether they're vehicles or structures alike. Meant to be dropped from high altitude, the Colossus features patented Atmo-Xact fins that deploy to provide additional guidance en route to target.
